131
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,230
I was worried about you.

132
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:15,020
If it weren't for the banquet at the Song Mansion,

133
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:17,310
if there weren't so many people at the banquet,

134
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:18,360
and if Thirteen and I hadn't

135
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,690
