139
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:26,180
Why didn't you

140
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:26,950
listen to me?

141
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:27,920
Why did you insist on staying?

142
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,760
Shen Nuo!

143
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,200
I saved you, and you're blaming me?

144
00:08:32,789 --> 00:08:33,850
What are you doing?

145
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:35,669
Lian Man'er, let me tell you.

146
00:08:36,409 --> 00:08:37,870
Pride comes before a fall.

147
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:40,470
Since I was there, I could protect you.

148
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,880
But when I'm not around in the future,

149
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:47,080
-and if you're still like this...
-When you're not around? Where can you go?

150
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:58,160
I just wanted to remind you that

151
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:01,180
before you make any decision in the future,

152
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,980
please think twice.

153
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,250
I think you're out of your mind.

154
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:09,090
You can't tell good from bad.

155
00:09:09,090 --> 00:09:10,080
Ridiculous.

156
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,260
Miss Lian.

157
00:09:12,430 --> 00:09:13,060
Miss Lian.

158
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:34,140
Why are you standing there and staring at me?

159
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:34,870
Nothing.

160
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,700
I just find it strange.

161
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,290
Young Master, I've been wondering

162
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:39,090
why you'd be willing

163
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:40,440
to stay in such a shabby room

164
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,740
for so long.

165
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:46,290
Are you still that Shen Nuo I used to know?

166
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,580
Young Master.

167
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:56,070
You like Miss Lian, don't you?

168
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:56,990
What are you talking about?

169
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:57,770
Then why

170
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,390
did you get so angry just now?

171
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,120
You wouldn't understand.

172
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:07,230
I don't, indeed.

173
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:24,230
Yu Xiangjin made such a big scene

174
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:25,690
at the Song Mansion today.

175
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:26,920
I think the troupe

176
00:10:27,110 --> 00:10:28,370
won't stay in the city.

177
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:31,450
They took the registration book.

178
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:33,510
We have to find a way to get it back.

179
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:35,700
I'll go to the Carters' Inn tomorrow

180
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:37,320
and see if I can find anything.

181
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,710
Okay, I'll go with you.

182
00:10:39,070 --> 00:10:39,590
No need.

183
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:41,760
Have a good rest.

184
