200
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:04,630
It's all because of Changsui.

201
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:05,820
It's because he didn't plan it carefully,

202
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,080
and he's incompetent.

203
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,100
I've tied him up and brought him here

204
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,230
